# [[separable]] [[verb]] (a type of Chinese verb which consists of two parts. The two parts may go together, or other words may be placed between the two parts. For example: [[睡觉]] (''shuìjiào'', to sleep) vs. [[睡]][[午|<font color="green">'''午'''</font>]][[觉]] (''shuì wǔ jiào'', take a noon nap).)

